{"tid":2454685,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國男子染疫後有超級抗體　抗體稀釋1萬倍仍有效殺死90%武肺病毒","createTime":"2021-03-20T11:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T05:44:38.000Z","uid":261647,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"f6f6e2cf288e7e99a0243a84c3b0335f0547d8ca","tid":2454685,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2910854/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2910854%2F&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDLYQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=335e9e06\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2910854/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2910000/2910854/antibody_thumb_20210319_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2910000%2F2910854%2Fantibody_thumb_20210319_ch_1024.jpg&h=d971fc71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情持續，各國紛紛研究對抗病毒的方法。美國有一名男子感染新冠肺炎後，擁有超級抗體，即使稀釋1萬倍仍有效殺死90%新冠病毒。<br />\n<br />\n染疫後快速痊癒<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報道，帶有超級抗體的男子John Hollis是非洲裔美國人，2020年3月他與兒子在封關前遊歐洲，回國後感到不適，情況不嚴重，幾日後就好轉了，以為是轉季而過敏，故不以為然。數星期後，與他同住的室友確診感染新冠肺炎，情況嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n當時他們對此症認知不多，但知道是可致命的。目睹室友的情況，他非常擔心，怕自己無法見證兒子繼續成長。最終室友康復，而John沒感到不適，也未知自己曾染疫，並有抗體。<br />\n<br />\n抗體稀釋1萬倍仍可殺死病毒<br />\n<br />\n直至去年7月，維珍尼亞州喬治梅森大學（George Mason University）的病理學家Lance Liotta博士展開新冠病毒抗體研究，邀請他參與，抽血、採集唾液檢測後，才發現他不僅曾感染新冠肺炎，而且體內更有可中和該病毒的超級抗體。<br />\n<br />\nLance Liotta博士更指，John Hollis的抗體很強，即使將其稀釋10,000倍仍能抵抗新冠病毒，而且可抵抗90％的新冠病毒。她又指，擁有超級抗體的患者或可抵抗南非、巴西及英國以外快速傳播的變種冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n另外在臨床試驗中，Lance Liotta的研究小組發現有另外7人體內有超級抗體。不過，這7人的抗體沒John Hollis那麼強，大多會在60至90天內消失，但John染疫9個月後，抗體有效率仍可保持90%。Lance Liotta博士表示，John Hollis的超級抗體有助下一階段臨床試驗，在已接種疫苗的人中進行測試。<br />\n<br />\nJohn Hollis被告知，每球擁有超級抗體的患者少於5%，其中只有約1%患者可中和任何病毒。他得知事實後，認為這是個超現實經歷，難以消化，一度承受壓力，但同時他為自己能保持健康而感到幸運。Lance Liotta博士表示，其研究團隊將繼續與John Hollis合作。"},{"pid":"7c22fa574387befb93cd2fa499fd4dd3fc070d35","tid":2454685,"uid":3980,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:57:27.000Z","msg":"要比人研究了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c066572ed45d7c3274b172474a9e632b7d9f7ab","tid":2454685,"uid":39780,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:58:20.000Z","msg":"黑鬼拯救世界<br />\n白人聽收皮"},{"pid":"ebc870ac1200fc684be0aafd6bfb3cc8d3ee7f93","tid":2454685,"uid":56624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:02:02.000Z","msg":"做咗新人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b589a1fcf4d43778b9f06123660b17c955242d6","tid":2454685,"uid":300690,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:04:07.000Z","msg":"The chosen one <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249bdafe1177e3fe38cc838bf1cb747c8a81621c","tid":2454685,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:04:34.000Z","msg":"會唔會俾人抽乾D血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17d704c053b153a18498a789fcf0c6dc5a79dd2","tid":2454685,"uid":40010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:07:23.000Z","msg":"支那準備好人民幣未"},{"pid":"062201e6c8f6e2e868ef248bcd2a7250d79db528","tid":2454685,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6oKYjC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6oKYjC.jpg&h=1d9fee92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a1a38323dfdd5ea22f2b11b00299e4d08df06b1","tid":2454685,"uid":82389,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:13:39.000Z","msg":"成日F F呢啲劇情會發生係自己身上，跟住就會發咗達，但估唔到現實真係有人發生咗"},{"pid":"2a928cefcb1c3de4a53cda1bc0231e3d7e138070","tid":2454685,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20